Acknowledgement
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

RaceIQ began from `mar-antaya/2025_f1_predictions` and has since been
substantially extended. The original author retains credit for the initial v1
framework.

See `docs/DATA_SOURCES.md` for the authoritative, version-controlled list with
links, roles, and usage notes.
